 SIM Card  In a statement yesterday in Abuja, the Technical Assistant (Information Technology) to the Minister of Communications and Digital Economy, Dr Femi Adeluyi, observed that the implementation of the policy would begin on Monday, April 19,2021, adding that issuance of new SIMs and other activities are resuming the same date once instruction had been obeyed. Adeluyi said his boss had also directed the Nigerian Communications Commission (NCC) and the Nigerian Information Management Commission (NIMC) to ensure that the policy was strictly adhered to by operators and subscribers. To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .